          <p>We may perform scheduled maintenance that temporarily affects service availability. We will provide advance notice when possible.</p>

          <h3>Support</h3>
          <p>Support is provided according to your service plan and our support policies.</p>

          <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          
          <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Our Services are provided "as is" without warranties</li>
            <li>We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
            <li>Our total liability is limited to the amount you paid in the 12 months preceding the claim</li>
